3Bdumb%26quot%3B%20bombs%2C%20a%20staggering%20statistic.%20But%20while%20the%20number%2C%20equating%20to%20thousands%20of%20devastating%20strikes%2C%20is%20shocking%2C%20Israel%20hasn't%20exactly%20hidden%20its%20use%20of%20the%20controversial%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20new%20assessment%20by%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%20on%20Israel's%20airstrikes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F12%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-israel-losing-support-netanyahu%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20that%20about%2040-45%25%20of%20the%2029%2C000%20air-to-ground%20munitions%20used%20in%20Gaza%20were%20unguided.%20The%20remainder%20were%20precision-guided%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20that%20Israel%20used%20upwards%20of%20over%2013%2C000%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bdumb%26quot%3B%20bombs%20in%20its%20devastating%20strikes%20in%20Gaza.%20Such%20weapons%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-air-force-photos-fighter-aircraft-armed-unguided-weapons-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edon't%20have%20internal%20guidance%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20kits%20to%20improve%20their%20aim%20and%20generally%20follow%20the%20trajectory%20at%20which%20they%20were%20dropped%2C%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20cause%20significant%20devastation%20beyond%20the%20intended%20target%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20which%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20continuous%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%2010%2F7%20Hamas%20terror%20attacks%20on%20October%207%2C%20thousands%20of%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20received%20some%20criticism%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20its%20suspected%20use%20of%20unguided%20munitions%20during%20the%20first%20week%20of%20its%20air%20campaign%20in%20Gaza.%20In%20early%20October%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20shared%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20fighter%20jets%20taking%20off%20for%20bombing%20campaigns%20with%20what%20experts%20quickly%20identified%20as%20unguided%20%26quot%3Bdumb%26quot%3B%20bombs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20open-source%20information%20accounts%20also%20documented%20the%20use%2C%20with%20one%20saying%20it%20that%20it%20suggested%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20may%20be%20dipping%20into%20stocks%20of%20older%2C%20less%20accurate%20unguided%20munitions.%26quot%3B%20But%20the%20IDF%20also%20shared%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20its%20bombs%20equipped%20with%20Joint%20Direct%20Attack%20Munitions%20(JDAMs)%20and%20other%20precision-guided%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20some%20of%20the%20precision%20weapons%2C%20due%20to%20the%20size%20of%20the%20bomb%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%202%2C000%20pounds%2C%20can%20do%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-pounding-gaza-massive-spice-kit-bombs-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserious%20damage%3C%2Fa%3E%20beyond%20the%20intended%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225808%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palestinian%20civilians%20and%20rescuers%20help%20clear%20the%20rubble%20in%20the%20heavily%20bombarded%20city%20center%20of%20Khan%20Yunis%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%20following%20overnight%20Israeli%20shelling%2C%20on%20October%2010%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b6aaf7a3c8094d5dd2fcd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223872%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalestinian%20civilians%20and%20rescuers%20help%20clear%20the%20rubble%20in%20the%20heavily%20bombarded%20city%20center%20of%20Khan%20Yunis%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%20following%20overnight%20Israeli%20shelling%2C%20on%20October%2010%2C%202023.%3Cp%3ESAID%20KHATIB%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20both%20its%20air%20and%20ground%20campaigns%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%94%20which%20have%20