military%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20ultimately%20allow%20Putin%20to%20take%20over%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHelping%20Ukraine%20hold%20the%20line%20against%20Russian%20forces%20through%20Western%20military%20aid%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bfar%20more%20advantageous%20and%20cheaper%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20US%20than%20if%20Ukraine%20were%20to%20lose%20the%20war%2C%20according%20to%20the%20war%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20in%20the%20US%20Congress%20have%20been%20blocking%20new%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2023%2F12%2F13%2Fremarks-by-president-biden-and-president-zelenskyy-of-ukraine-in-joint-press-conference-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccusing%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20of%20holding%20the%20funding%20%26quot%3Bhostage%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20%26quot%3Bforce%20through%20an%20extreme%20Republican%20partisan%20agenda%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20US-Mexico%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20Republicans%20say%20they%20want%20tougher%20immigration%20politics%20and%20more%20funding%20for%20border%20security%20in%20exchange%20for%20helping%20Ukraine%2C%20other%20right-wing%20lawmakers%20have%20ruled%20out%20giving%20Ukraine%20any%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ISW%2C%20a%20Russian%20take-over%20of%20all%20of%20Ukraine%20%26quot%3Bis%20by%20no%20means%20impossible%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20US%20cuts%20off%20all%20military%20aid%20and%20Europe%20follows%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20an%20outcome%20would%20bring%20a%20battered%20but%20triumphant%20Russian%20army%20right%20up%20to%20NATO's%20border%20from%20the%20Black%20Sea%20to%20the%20Arctic%20Ocean%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20war%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20would%20mean%20that%20the%20US%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20deploy%20a%20%26quot%3Bsizable%20portion%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20ground%20forces%20to%20Eastern%20Europe%20to%20%26quot%3Bdeter%20an