looking%20for%20a%20dedicated%20wired%20headset%20on%20a%20budget%2C%20we%20recommend%20the%20Turtle%20Beach%20Recon%2070.%20It's%20an%20entry-level%20headset%20with%20a%20swivel%20microphone%20and%20plastic%20shell.%20The%20headset%20offers%20nine%20color%20options%2C%20which%20helps%20make%20it%20a%20solid%20choice%20for%20younger%20gamers%20who%20want%20a%20variety%20of%20looks%20to%20choose%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Recon%2070%20connects%20to%20the%20PS5%20via%20the%20DualSense%20controller%20and%20is%20fully%20compatible%20with%203D%20audio%2C%20but%20you'll%20have%20to%20use%20the%20console's%20on-screen%20settings%20to%20manage%20volume%20and%20audio%20balance.%20The%20microphone%20automatically%20mutes%20when%20swiveled%20up%20away%20from%20your%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wired%20sound%20quality%20matches%20what%20we%20expect%20to%20hear%20when%20using%20the%20PS5's%203D%20audio%20tech%2C%20and%20the%20microphone%20quality%20is%20up%20to%20par%20in%20voice%20chat%20as%20well.%20While%20the%20audio%20profile%20boosts%20bass%2C%20the%20sound%20is%20not%20quite%20as%20deep%20as%20the%20more%20expensive%20headsets%20we%20recommend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plastic%20build%20also%20makes%20the%20Recon%2070%20feel%20less%20durable%20than%20pricier%20headsets%3B%20it's%20sturdy%20enough%20to%20last%20through%20hours%20of%20regular%20play%20at%20home%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20be%20the%20best%20option%20to%20take%20on%20the%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20earbuds%3Cp%3EThe%20Razer%20Hammerhead%20Pro%20HyperSpeed%20are%20one%20of%20the%20few%20pairs%20of%20wireless%20gaming%20headphones%20that%20use%20an%20earbud-style%20design.%20While%20the%20case%20and%20form%20factor%20may%20make%20them%20look%20similar%20to%20something%20like%20Apple's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fapple-airpods-2nd-generation-review%5C%22%3EAirPods%20Pros%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Hammerheads%20are%20larger%20and%20include%20support%20f