20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20physical%20build%20of%20a%20PS5%20headset%20is%20important%20for%20its%20longevity%2C%20so%20we%20check%20for%20overall%20comfort%2C%20battery%20life%2C%20sturdiness%2C%20and%20the%20materials%20used.%20Other%20factors%20of%20the%20design%20are%20important%20too%2C%20like%20microphone%20placement%2C%20storage%2C%20RGB%20lighting%2C%20and%20alternate%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%20and%20connectivity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20the%20PS5%20supports%20lots%20of%20headsets%20and%20even%20standard%20headphones%2C%20they%20don't%20all%20offer%20the%20same%20range%20of%20features.%20We%20look%20for%20features%20like%20simultaneous%20Bluetooth%20and%20noise%20cancellation%20and%20prioritize%20range%20and%20cross-compatibility%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EValue%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20best%20PS5%20headsets%20can%20cost%20as%20much%20as%20%24350%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20spend%20that%20much%20to%20take%20home%20a%20great%20headset.%20We%20judge%20headsets%20by%20comparing%20the%20overall%20performance%20and%20quality%20against%20the%20asking%20price%3B%20feature-rich%20headsets%20with%20competitive%20prices%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20make%20our%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPS5%20headset%20FAQs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20SteelSeries%20Arctis%20Nova%20Pro%20Wireless%20gaming%20headset%20on%20a%20wood%20surface%20resting%20against%20the%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F649c61976eb0a800194d7efb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20Webb%20%2F%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20wireless%20gaming%20headsets%20have%20disadvantages%20compared%20to%20wired%20ones%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20wireless%20headphone%20technology%20used%20to%20have%20bigger%20limitations%2C%20modern%202.4GHz%20wireless%20signals%20no%20longer%2