20was%20discovered%20on%20September%201%20after%20Discord%20reported%20the%20teenager%20to%20the%20FBI.%20The%20investigation%20led%20to%20the%20teenager's%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiscord's%20Counter-Extremism%20analysts%20proactively%20detected%2C%20removed%2C%20and%20reported%20this%20user%20to%20the%20FBI's%20National%20Threat%20Operations%20Center%2C%20which%20is%20what%20led%20to%20the%20user's%20arrest.%20We%20have%20a%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20against%20hate%20and%20violent%20extremism%2C%20and%20when%20we%20see%20it%2C%20we%20take%20immediate%20action.%20It%20is%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20Discord%20to%20ensure%20a%20safe%20experience%20for%20our%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Redgrave%2C%20Discord's%20vice%20president%20of%20trust%C2%A0%26amp%3B%20safety%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fdiscord-tips-off-fbi-13-year-olds-synagogue%2Fstory%3Fid%3D105647160%5C%22%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20publicly%20named%20because%20he's%20a%20minor%2C%20now%20faces%20juvenile%20misdemeanor%20charges%20of%20inducing%20panic%20and%20disorderly%20conduct.%20He%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20trial%20on%20December%2020%20in%20Stark%20County%20Family%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20any%20weapons%20were%20found%20when%20the%20teenager%20was%20arrested%2C%20and%20how%20serious%20his%20intentions%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0statement%C2%A0from%20the%20Anti-Defamation%20League's%20chapter%20in%20Cleveland%2C%20about%2060%20miles%20from%20Ohio%2C%20said%20the%20group%20was%20''horrified''%20to%20learn%20of%20the%20plans%20to%20shoot%20up%20Temple%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''For%20young%20people%20like%20this%20suspect%2C%20we%20hope%20this%20can%20be%20a%20teachable%20moment.%20Hate%20and%20threats%20on%20social%20media%2C%20as%20in%20real%20life%2C%20cannot%20and%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%2C''%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2023%2Fdec%2F14%2Fteen-arrested-mass-shooting-plan-ohio-synagogue%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThey%20also%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethanked%20law%20enforcement%20for%20the%20''thorough%20investigation.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20came%20more%20than%20a%20month%20before%20Hamas'%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel%20and%20Israel's%20ensuing%20war%20in%20Gaza.%20According%20to%20recent%20FBI%20statistics%2C%20antisemitic%20hate%20crimes%20rose%2025%20percent%20from%202021%20to%202022.%C2%A0The%20Anti-Defamation%20League%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20advocates%20against%20antisemitism%2C%20said%20they%20received%20reports%20of%203%2C697%20antisemitic%20incidents%20across%20the%20US%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702578060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Flmb8dlvo_temple-israel-canton_625x300_14_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-boy-13-charged-after-allegedly-plotting-a-mass-shooting-at-synagogue-4675399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20court%20documents%2C%20the%20teenager%20was%20allegedly%20devising%20a%20plan%20to%20''complete%20a%20mass%20shooting''%20at%20Temple%20Israel%20in%20Canton%2C%20Ohio%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-boy-13-charged-after-allegedly-plotting-a-mass-shooting-at-synagogue-4675399%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-boy-13-charged-after-allegedly-plotting-a-mass-shooting-at-synagogue-4675399%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-boy-13-charged-after-allegedly-plotting-a-mass-shooting-at-synagogue-4675399%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mastermind%20Of%20Parliament%20Security%20Breach%20Surrenders%20To%20Delhi%20Police%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELalit%20Jha%2C%20the%20alleged%20mastermind%20of%20the%20security%20breach%20in%20parliament%20that%20shocked%20the%20nation%2C%20has%20surrendered.%20Sources%20said%20he%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20police%20station%20on%20Kartavya%20Path%20(the%20boulevard%20renamed%20'Path%20of%20Duty'%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Delhi)%20and%20surrendered.%20He%20has%20been%20formally%20arrested%20and%20the%20New%20Delhi%20District%20Police%20has%20handed%20him%20over%20to%20the%20Special%20Cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkata-based%20teacher%20was%20arrested%20from%20Delhi%20after%20being%20on%20the%20run%20for%20nearly%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20man%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20gone%20by%20bus%20to%20Rajasthan's%20Nagaur%20via%20Neemrana%20--%20where%20he%20he%20was%20seen%20last%20--%20and%20stayed%20at%20a%20hotel%20with%20two%20friends.%20Later%2C%20when%20he%20realised%20that%20the%20police%20were%20looking%20for%20him%2C%20he%20came%20back.%20At%20the%20police%20station%20today%2C%20he%20was%20accompanied%20by%20one%20Mahesh%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20persons%20were%20arrested%20for%20yesterday%20afternoon's%20security%20breach%20in%20which%20two%20men%20--%20Sagar%20and%20Manoranjan%20--%20smuggled%20in%20smoke%20bombs%20and%20let%20them%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sbaha%20proceedings.%20Two%20others%2C%20Neelam%20Devi%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%2C%20who%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20get%20a%20pass%2C%20held%20a%20protest%20outside%20the%20parliament%20building%2C%20shouting%20slogans%20and%20waving%20smoke%20canisters%2C%20before%20they%20were%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalit%20Jha%2C%20who%20also%20did%20not%20get%20a%20visitors'%20pass%2C%20recorded%20it%20on%20his%20cellphone%20and%20uploaded%20it%20on%20social%20media.%20He%20also%20passed%20on%20a%20copy%20to%20a%20Kolkata-based%20associate%20who%20runs%20a%20non-profit%2C%20investigators%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20motive%20of%20the%20unprecedented%20%26quot%3Bsmoke%20protest%26quot%3B%2C%20investigators%20said%2C%20was%20to%20highlight%20the%20growing%20unemployment%2C%20plight%20of%20farmers%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20group%20wanted%20a%20discussion%20on%20these%20matters%20in%20parliament%20and%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20a%20flashy%20way%20to%20draw%20attention.%20The%20group%20were%20part%20of%20a%20Facebook%20page%20called%20%26quot%3BFans%20of%20Bhagat%20Singh%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20also%20said%20off%20the%20record%20that%20there%20appeared%20to%20be%20no%20organised%20terror%20group%20behind%20the%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20court%2C%20though%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20earlier%20said%20the%20matter%20needs%20further%20investigation%20while%20seeking%20two%20week's%20custody%20of%20the%20four%20people%20arrested.%20The%20accused%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20the%20anti-terror%20law%20UAPA%20and%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20contended%20that%20the%20whole%20operation%20resembled%20a%20terror%20attack%20and%20questioned%20the%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWas%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20incident%20only%20to%20express%20one's%20point%20or%20to%20carry%20out%20some%20major%20incident%3F%20It%20has%20to%20be%20investigated%20whether%20any%20terrorist%20organisation%20is%20involved%20in%20this%20entire%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20allowed%20them%20a%20week's%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702577940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fapbffss8_lalit-jha-parliament-security-breach_625x300_14_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmastermind-of-parliament-security-breach-arrested-in-delhi-4675060%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lalit%20Jha%2C%20the%20alleged%20mastermind%20of%20the%20s