3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEither%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20deceased%20can%20accept%20the%20bodies%20and%20perform%20the%20last%20rites%20at%20any%20of%20the%20nine%20burial%20sites%20identified%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%20or%20the%20state%20can%20go%20ahead%20and%20do%20the%20same%20in%20accordance%20with%20municipal%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20had%20ordered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inability%20of%20family%20members%20to%20travel%20within%20the%20state%20to%20collect%20the%20bodies%20of%20their%20relatives%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%20has%20been%20a%20continual%20reminder%20of%20the%20divide%20in%20the%20state%20with%20almost%20no%20serious%20attempts%20to%20restore%20amity%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20state%20government%20run%20by%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20or%20that%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%2C%20bodies%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20that%20were%20in%20Imphal%20were%20sent%20back%20to%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Churachandpur%20district%20via%20air-ambulance.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmanipur_police%2Fstatus%2F1735338636953207227%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EThe%20Manipur%20police%20late%20at%20night%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20dead%20bodies%20of%20the%20deceased%20persons%20in%20c%2Fw%20the%20present%20violence%20in%20the%20State%20which%20had%20been%20kept%20preserved%20at%20the%20mortuaries%20of%20District%20Hospital%20Churachandpur%2C%20RIMS%20and%20JNIMS%20have%20been%20relocated%20to%20their%20respective%20hometowns%20or%20preferred%20locations%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20for%20their%20final%20rites.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20confirmed%20that%20%E2%80%9C41%20bodies%20to%20Churachandpur%2C%2019%20bodies%20to%20Kangpokpi%20from%20JNIMS%20and%20RIMS%20Imphal%20and%2004%20bodies%20from%20Churachandpur%20to%20Imphal%20have%20been%20relocated%20for%20handing%20over%20to%20next%20of%20kin%20of%20the%20deceased%20persons.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20200%20lives%20have%20been%20claimed%20by%20the%20violence%20so%20far.%20The%20numbers%20include%20those%20who%20have%20died%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20medical%20facilities.%20Furthermore%2C%20both%20communities%20are%20discussing%20the%20whereabouts%20and%20probable%20fates%20of%20missing%20persons%20of%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Soibam%20Ibohal%20from%20the%20International%20Meitei%20Organisation%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20still%2022%20missing%20persons%20from%20our%20community%2C%20including%20those%20two%20children%20(Luwangbi%20Linthoingambi%20Hijam%20and%20Phijam%20Hemanjit%20Singh)%20who%20went%20to%20coaching%20class%20and%20never%20came%20back.%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftheir-children-missing-and-the-authorities-silent-two-manipuri-families-dont-know-where-to-turn%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20two%20young%20persons%20who%20had%20gone%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20side%2C%20there%20are%20at%20least%20nine%20missing%20persons%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community.%20In%20a%20press%20note%2C%20COTU%2C%20a%20Civil%20Society%20Group%2C%20informed%20the%20media%20about%20the%20cremation%20ceremony%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20at%20Phaijang%20village%20in%20Kangpokpi%20on%20December%2015.%20The%20bodies%20sent%20to%20Kangpokpi%20also%20include%20the%20bodies%20of%20three%20Kuki%20women%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20Imphal%2C%20and%20their%20case%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation.%20COTU%20has%20also%20declared%20a%20full%2012-hour%20shutdown%20from%205%20am%20to%205%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20announcement%20so%20far%20from%20Churachandpur%20about%20the%20burial%20of%20the%20bodies%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20violence%20i