w.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmha-orders-probe-into-parliament-security-breach-incident-2809994%5C%22%3Eheaded%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Anish%20Dayal%20Singh%2C%20CRPF%20chief.%20Incidentally%2C%20perimeter%20security%20of%20Parliament%20comes%20under%20the%20paramilitary%20force%20that%20Singh%20heads.%20The%20probe%20panel%20includes%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20frisking%20visitors%20to%20Parliament%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20refused%20to%20let%20both%20Houses%20function%2C%2014%20opposition%20MPs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-rajnath-singh-opposition-statement-amit-shah%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20So%20far%2C%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Mysuru%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%2C%20who%20issued%20the%20visitors%20gallery%20pass%20to%20the%20two%20men%20who%20intruded%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Many%20pointed%20to%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%2C%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20for%20sharing%20her%20credentials%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20website%20with%20her%20staff.%20The%20number%20was%20initially%2015%20till%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20office%20realised%20that%20one%20of%20the%20MPs%20was%20not%20even%20in%20town%20when%20he%20was%20suspended%20for%20disrupting%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-yellow-smoke-signals-tell-us-about-the-mother-of-democracy%5C%22%3EWhat%20Yellow%20Smoke%20Signals%20Tell%20Us%20About%20the%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESivaganga%20MP%20Karti%20Chidambaram%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20this%20government%2C%20it%20is%20business%20as%20usual.%20They%20are%20behaving%20as%20if%20we%20are%20hallucinating%20and%20nothing%20really%20happened.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20underplay%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation.%20The%20gas%20could%20have%20been%20lethal.%20The%20fact%20is%2C%20this%20was%20meticulously%20planned.%20They%20beat%20the%20system%20and%20the%20so-called%20foolproof%20security.%20And%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20knee-jerk%20reaction.%20Ban%20visitors%2C%20ban%20journalists%20is%20their%20answer%20as%20is%20banning%20MPs%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20present%20there.%20This%20government%20cant%20recognise%20one%20Tamil%20from%20another.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20eight%20persons%20on%20deputation%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Secretariat%20have%20been%20suspended%20and%20security%20beefed%20up.%20The%20%3Cem%3Emakar%20dwar%3C%2Fem%3E%20used%20by%20visitors%20and%20MPs%20alike%20is%20out%20of%20bounds%20for%20journalists%2C%20and%20visitors%20are%20banned%20altogether%2C%20as%20is%20the%20staff%20of%20MPs.%20Access%20control%20to%20the%20complex%20has%20been%20tightened%20with%20pass%20holders%20being%20allowed%20in%20only%20from%20the%20transport%20bhavan%20side%20and%20Delhi%20Police%20could%20be%20seen%20frisking%20bystanders%20near%20the%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%20(December%2013)%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20robust%20contingent%20of%20RAF%20and%20other%20paramilitary%20and%20security%20forces%2C%20one%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20Neelam%20Verma%20%E2%80%98Azad%E2%80%99%20released%20smoke%20from%20a%20canister%20and%20shouted%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20four%20of%20the%20six%20have%20been%20placed%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20the%20location%20of%20the%20sixth%20person%2C%20Lalit%2C%20was%20found%20to%20be%20Neemrana%2C%20from%20where%20he%20sent%20the%20video%20of%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20incident%2C%20which%20he%20filmed%2C%20to%20a%20friend.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fparliament-security-breach-mastermind-lalit-jha-arrested-in-delhi%2Farticleshow%2F106000305.cms%5C%22%3Ewas%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Delhi%20this%20evening%20(December%2014).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfluenced%20by%20revolutionary%20freedom%20fighter%20Bhagat%20Singh%20who%2C%20too%2C%20had%20thrown%20a%20bomb%20from%20the%20old%20Parliament%20building%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20visitors%20gallery%2C%20the%20accused%20wanted%20to%20draw%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20government%2C%20they%20said%2C%20to%20issues%20of%20unemployment%2C%20the%20Manipur%20issue%2C%20farmers%E2%80%99%20crisis%2C%20and%20autocracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20remand%20application%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fparliament-breach-act-a-well-planned-conspiracy-delhi-police-tell-court%2Farticle67638548.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20court%20that%20the%20accused%20wanted%20to%20give%20a%20pamphlet%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20calling%20him%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%20person%E2%80%9D.%20The%20pamphlet%20also%20offered%20a%20cash%20award%20from%20a%20Swiss%20bank.%20The%20canisters%20were%20bought%20from%20Mumbai%20and%20the%20shoes%20from%20Lucknow%2C%20the%20police%20told%20the%20court%20as%20it%20sought%20a%20custody%20of%2015%20days%20to%20uncover%20a%20possible%20terrorist%20angle.%20The%20police%20said%20such%20an%20attack%20would%20have%20had%20the%20backing%20of%20a%20larger%20organization.%20The%20court%20granted%20a%20weeks%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20full%20body%20scanners%20will%20now%20be%20part%20of%20the%20security%20protocol%2C%20a%20move%20that%20the%20present%20government%20had%20staunchly%20opposed%20while%20in%20the%20opposition.%20Issues%20raised%20about%20individual%20privacy%20was%20one%20reason%20a%20proposal%20to%20install%20scanners%20at%20all%20airports%20had%20then%20been%20shelved%20but%20was%20later%20revived%20quietly%20three%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20said%20they%20will%20not%20allow%20Parliament%20to%20function%20till%20the%20home%20min