%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdistraction%20for%20eight%20months%20before%20ending%20all%20communication%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20French%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Lenain%2C%20who%20is%20now%20France%E2%80%99s%20ambassador%20to%20Brazil%2C%20felt%20compelled%20to%20write%20a%20diplomatic%20note%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20diplomatic%20note%2C%20he%20also%20mentioned%20that%20the%20French%20government%20used%20the%20%E2%80%9Copportunity%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20G20%20anti-corruption%20summit%E2%80%9D%20on%20August%2011th%20and%2012th%20in%20Kolkata%20to%20try%20to%20%E2%80%9Cadvance%20certain%20cases%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMediapart%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F060421%2Frafale-jets-sale-india-macron-hollande-and-blind-eye-frances-anti-corruption-services%5C%22%3Ehad%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F140922%2Frafale-papers-french-judges-face-military-secrecy-hurdles-over-probe-sale-fighters%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20the%20French%20and%20Indian%20governments%20are%20united%20in%20their%20desire%20to%20slow%20down%20a%20highly%20sensitive%20investigation%20that%20could%20implicate%20three%20heads%20of%20state%20or%20government%3A%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20French%20president%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20his%20predecessor%20at%20the%20%C3%89lys%C3%A9e%20Fran%C3%A7ois%20Hollande.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202018%2C%20the%20French%20investigating%20judges%20had%20requested%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20send%20them%20judicial%20documents%20concerning%20Dassault%20and%20Sushen%20Gupta%2C%20an%20influential%20defence%20businessman%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsushen-gupta-agent-rafale-deal-ed%5C%22%3Ewas%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20the%20alleged