20been%20taken%20against%20that%20MP.%20Whereas%20we%20saw%20what%20happened%20in%20Mahua%E2%80%99s%20case.%20Without%20even%20the%20inquiry%20being%20complete%2C%20she%20has%20been%20disqualified%20and%20this%20MP%20is%20not%20even%20suspended.%20He%E2%80%99s%20inside%20Parliament%20with%20us.%20And%20when%20we%20protested%20and%20we%20want%20the%20PM%20and%20the%20Home%20Minister%20to%20come%20and%20give%20a%20statement%20in%20the%20House%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20prepared%20to%20do%20that.%20And%20when%20we%20protested%2C%20they%20are%20suspending%20all%20the%20opposition%20MPs.%20First%20suspended%20five%2C%20then%20they%20suspended%20nine%20people.%20So%20how%20is%20this%20democracy%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlier%20events%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20termed%20the%20security%20breach%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%20and%20called%20for%20all%20parliamentarians%20to%20exercise%20caution%20in%20issuing%20passes%20while%20opposition%20MPs%20moved%20to%20the%20well%20of%20the%20house%20chanting%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9Cshame%2C%20shame%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanding%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20home%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20December%2013%2C%20two%20men%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-anniversary-slogan-dictatorship%5C%22%3Ejumped%20from%20the%20public%20gallery%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20hall%20and%20opened%20smoke%20canisters%2C%20causing%20House%20proceedings%20to%20be%20interrupted.%20The%20security%20breach%20occurred%20on%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20attack%20on%20the%20parliament%2C%20then%20housed%20in%20a%20different%20building.%20The%20two%20who%20entered%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20received%20their%20entry%20passes%20from%20BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%20and%20shouted%20slogans%20but%20did%20not%20attempt%20to%20harm%20anyone%20in%20the%20hall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20protests%20from%20opposition%20MPs%2C%20Singh%20rose%20from%20his%20chair%20and%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20is%20quite%20unfortunate%2C%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%20You%20(speaker)%20took%20immediate%20note%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20ordered%20a%20probe.%20I%20believe%20that%20all%20MPs%20both%20from%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20government%20need%20to%20maintain%20caution.%20So%20that%20passes%20are%20not%20issued%20to%20people%20who%20then%20go%20ahead%20and%20spread%20anarchy%20in%20the%20house.%20You%20have%20already%20ordered%20a%20probe%20and%20other%20precautionary%20measures%20that%20can%20be%20taken%20in%20the%20future%20will%20be%20done%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20concerns%20raised%20by%20opposition%20MPs%20over%20the%20security%20measures%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%2C%20Singh%20said%20that%20such%20incidents%20had%20also%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20old%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20want%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20the%20old%20parliament%20building%20also%20saw%20similar%20incidents%20including%20throwing%20papers%20into%20the%20well%20of%20the%20house%20as%20well%20as%20jumping.%20All%20MPs%20should%20condemn%20the%20incident.%20Since%20a%20probe%20has%20been%20ordered%20and%20future%20measures%20are%20being%20looked%20into%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20spread%20anarchic%20conditions%20inside%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Delhi%20police%20have%20arrested%20five%20people%20in%20total%3A%20Sagar%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20D%2C%20the%20two%20men%20who%20entered%20the%20house%3B%20as%20well%20as%20two%20others%20who%20protested%20outside%20parliament%2C%20identified%20as%20Amol%20Shinde%20and%20Neelam%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20individual%2C%20Vikram%2C%20was%20arrested%20as%20a%20suspected%20accomplice.%20As%20sixth%20person%2C%20Lalit%2C%20was%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDerek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20suspended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Thursday%2C%20opposition%20members%20demanded%20a%20short-term%20discussion%20on%20the%20security%20breach%20the%20day%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajya%20Sabha%20chair%20and%20vice%20president%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar%20informed%20the%20house%20that%20he%20had%20received%2026%20notices%20%E2%80%93%20including%20from%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20%E2%80%93%20demanding%20suspension%20of%20business%20to%20discuss%20the%20security%20breach%20but%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20find%20merit%20in%20the%20notices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20houses%20were%20adjourned%20within%20an%20hour%20of%20proceedings%20starting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20resumed%20proceedings%20at%20noon%2C%20Dhankar%20accused%20TMC%20MP%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgross%20misconduct%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cgross%20defiance%20of%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20chair.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20suspended%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20session%20after%20a%20motion%20was%20moved%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Piyush%20Goyal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoyal%20said%20that%20the%20house%20%E2%80%9Chaving%20taken%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20misconduct%20of%20Shri%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20member%20who%20has%20entered%20the%20well%20of%20the%20house%20and%20has%20been%20continuously%20shouting%20slogans%2C%20gesticulating%20aggressively%20at%20the%20chair%20thereby%20disrupting%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20house%20in%20utter%20disregard%20to%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20chair%20and%20having%20been%20named%20by%20the%20chair%E2%80%9D%20be%20suspended.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20sloganeering%20from%20opposition%20members%20after%20O%E2%80%99Brien%E2%80%99s%20suspension%2C%20Dhankar%20adjourned%20the%20proceedings%20till%202%20pm.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20opposition%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20also%20held%20a%20meeting%20before%20the%20session%20started%20to%20discuss%20the%20security%20breach.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20parties%20demanded%20a%20detailed%20statement%20by%20Shah%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%2C%20as%20well%20as%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%20%E2%80%93%20who%20provided%20the%20visitor%20passes%20to%20the%20intruders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20INDIA%20parties%20are%20demanding%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20A%20detailed%20statement%20by%20the%20Home%20Minister%20in%20both%20Houses%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20very%20serious%20and%20shocking%20security%20breach%20witnessed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Strict%20action%20against%20the%20BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%20who%20provided%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1735182565567308169%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20accept%20these%20perfectly%20legitimate%20and%20reasonable%20demands%20has%20led%20to%20the%20adjournment%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E14%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20suspended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20proceedings%20resumed%20at%202%20pm%2C%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20accused%20%E2%80%9Csome%20members%20of%20politicising%E2%80%9D%20the%20issue%2C%20before%20moving%20a%20motion%20to%20suspend%20five%20Congress%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20he%20agrees%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20unfortunate%20incident%E2%80%9D%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20MPs%2C%20he%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Cappreciate%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20honourable%20speaker%20promptly%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20all%20floor%20leaders%20and%20listened%20to%20their%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20security%20of%20the%20parliament%20premises.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20suggestions%20given%20have%20already%20been%20implemented.%20As%20the%20speaker%20observed%20this%20morning%20also%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20further%20measures%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20strengthen%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20security.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20this%20matter%20concerns%20us%20all%20and%20we%20have%20to%20speak%20in%20one%20voice%20on%20such%20a%20grave%20national%20issue.%20No%20politics%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20done%20by%20anyone%20on%20such%20grave%20issues.%20We%20have%20to%20rise%20above%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoshi%20then%20went%20on%20to%20list%20the%20previous%20incidents%20of%20security%20breaches%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20many%20such%20incidents%20have%20taken%20place.%20I%20am%20not%20comparing%20past%20incidents%20and%20defending%20today%E2%80%99s%20incident%20but%20we%20have%20to%20learn%20lessons%20from%20our%20past%20to%20bring%20a%20bright%20future.%20On%20April%2011%2C%201974%2C%20one%20person%20named%20Ratan%20Chandra%20Gupta%20one%20person%20shouted%20slogans%20from%20the%20visitors%E2%80%99%20gallery%20while%20carrying%20two%20pistols.%20In%20July%201974%2C%20Biplab%20Basu%20was%20found%20carrying%20a%20dagger%20hidden%20on%20his%20person%20and%20tried%20to%20enter%20the%20visitors%E2%80%99%20gallery.%20On%20November%2026%2C%201974%2C%20Satyajit%20Singh%20carried%20explosives%20and%20a%20dagger%20hidden%20on%20his%20person%20to%20the%20visitors%E2%80%99%20gallery.%20On%20January%209%20and%2010%2C%201999%2C%20Badri%20Prasad%20and%20Pushpendra%20Chavan%20jumped%20from%20the%20gallery%20to%20the%20chamber%20of%20Lok%20Sabha.%20As%20I%20have%20already%20said%20we%20are%20not%20comparing%20but%20these%20kinds%20of%20unfortunate%20incidents%20have%20been%20happening%20since%20beginning-shouting%20slogans%2C%20throwing%20paper%20and%20jumping%20from%20the%20gallery.%20I%20have%20many%20such%20incidents%20%5Bto%20list%5D.%20We%20all%20understand%20that%20parliament%20is%20for%20protecting%20the%20immunity%20and%20efficient%20discharge%20of%20functions.%20Internal%20security%20is%20under%20the%20speaker.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20such%20matters%20have%20been%20dealt%20with%20by%20directions%20of%20the%20speaker.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20appropriate%20agencies%20would%20be%20dealing%20with%20the%20incident%20as%20per%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20and%20that%20the%20speaker%20had%20already%20written%20to%20the%20home%20secretary%20for%20a%20high-level%20enquiry%20which%20has%20already%20been%20initiated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20also%20very%20sensitive%20to%20these%20matters%20so%20I%20urge%20you%20to%20allow%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20house%20to%20take%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20added%20that%20it%20has%20become%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20habit%20of%20some%20members%20to%20politicise%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20moved%20a%20resolution%20to%20suspend%20five%20Congress%20MPs%20T.N.%20Prathapan%2C%20Hibi%20Eden%2C%20S.%20Jothimani%2C%20Ramya%20Haridas%20and%20Dean%20Kuriakose%20for%20%E2%80%9Cutter%20disregard%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20house%20and%20undermining%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20house%20resumed%20at%203%20pm%2C%20Joshi%20moved%20a%20resolution%20to%20suspend%20nine%20more%20opposition%20MPs%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Manickam%20Tagore%2C%20Mohammad%20Jawed%20and%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20Kanimozhi%20and%20S.R.%20Parthiban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20then%20adjourned%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20article%20was%20updated%20after%20it%20was%20published.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702547383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14145946%2FScreenshot-2023-12-14-at-2.59.04%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-rajnath-singh-opposition-statement-amit-shah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20asked%20the%20oppoisition%20members%20not%20to%20'politicise%20the%20issue'%20and%20listed%20past%20instances%20of%20such%20breaches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-rajnath-singh-opposition-statement-amit-shah%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%20Royals%20owner%20goes%20into%20bat%20with%20%24650m%20valuation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702547340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-root-rajasthan-royals_6392617.jpg%3F20231214095551%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frajasthan-royals-owner-goes-into-bat-with-650m-valuation-13030092%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20majority-owner%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20Indian%20cricket%20franchise%20has%20struck%20a%20deal%20to%20sell%20a%20stake%20at%20a%20%24650m%20valuation%2C%20underlining%20the%20surge%20in%20investor%20interest%20in%20the%20sport's%20newest%20formats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frajasthan-royals-owner-goes-into-bat-with-650m-valuation-13030092%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Frajasthan-royals-owner-goes-into-bat-with-650m-valuation-13030092%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Frajasthan-royals-owner-goes-into-bat-with-650m-valuation-13030092%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%3A%20Russia%20can't%20exist%20without%20sovereignty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702546439000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FF54A%2Fproduction%2F_132049726_p0gzg602.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67714359%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20president%20vows%20to%20strengthen%20Russia's%20sovereignty%20as%20he%20starts%20a%20lengthy%20press%20conference.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-europe-67714359%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Art%2C%20Architecture%20and%20Design%20Biennale%3A%20The%20Fine%20Line%20Between%20Government%20Support%20and%20Politicisation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14121410%2FH20231208146124.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20great%20things%20about%20art%20has%20always%20been%20the%20impossibility%20of%20a%20logical%20definition.%20A%20dead%20butterfly%20was%20as%20much%20art%2C%20as%20it%20was%20a%20biological%20phenomenon%3B%20a%20pear%20was%20a%20nutritious%20fruit%20and%20also%20a%20delicate%20still-life%20painting.%20When%20art%20loses%20these%20multiple%20meanings%2C%20it%20drops%20a%20few%20notches%20from%20philosophy%20to%20science%20to%20mere%20data%2C%20thereby%20also%20losing%20the%20essential%20element%20of%20redundancy%20that%20keeps%20it%20alive%20and%20well%20and%20kicking.%20When%20governments%20enter%20the%20fray%2C%20art%20begins%20to%20flounder%20further.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20week%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1985002%5C%22%3Einauguration%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20India%20Art%20Architecture%20and%20Design%20Biennale%20(IAADB)%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Red%20Fort%20set%20off%20alarm%20bells%20amongst%20several%20artists%20and%20writers.%20An%20official%20endorsement%20by%20the%20government%20of%20what%20constitutes%20Indian%20art%20and%20design%20is%20not%20just%20troubling%20from%20the%20standpoint%20of%20its%20content%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20art%20should%20be%20so%20brazenly%20claimed%20by%20the%20government.%20It%20has%20taken%20many%20decades%20to%20establish%20a%20notable%20independence%20from%20political%20patronage%2C%20but%20this%20official%20government%20support%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20ready%20acceptance%20by%20many%20artists%20and%20supposedly%20autonomous%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20comes%20as%20a%20surprise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20to%20say%20that%20government%20funds%20are%20not%20required%20for%20the%20arts%2C%20but%20it%20does%20stand%20to%20reason%20that%20bureaucratic%20support%20and%20money%20should%20ideally%20go%20where%20most%20needed.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1794907%5C%22%3EAtmanirbhar%20Bharat%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E%20established%20in%20support%20of%20traditional%20artists%20and%20crafts%20is%20a%20commendable%20recent%20initiative%20to%20keep%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20crafts%20alive%2C%20especially%20so%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20elite%20arts%20of%20painting%2C%20sculpture%2C%20installation%2C%20etc.%2C%20are%20now%20either%20wholly%20international%20or%20receive%20enough%20support%20from%20private%20galleries%20and%20foundations.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20revival%20of%20dying%20practices%20and%20struggling%20folk%20traditions%20is%20a%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction%3B%20the%20politicisation%20of%20art%2C%20however%2C%20is%20an%20altogether%20different%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECertainly%2C%20Biennales%20in%20Venice%2C%20Singapore%20and%20Dubai%20all%20receive%20city%20and%20federal%20support%2C%20but%20they%20are%20run%20as%20autonomous%20private%20events%2C%20without%20bureaucracy%20or%20government%20presence.%20Even%20national%20museums%20and%20galleries%20in%20the%20US%20which%20get%20federal%20funding%20remain%20independent%20and%20entirely%20free%20to%20select%20and%20showcase%20art.%20In%20the%201980s%2C%20when%20the%20Gallery%20of%20American%20Art%20placed%20a%20burger%20stand%20and%20McDonald%E2%80%99s%20arches%20in%20an%20exhibition%20on%20ordinary%20American%20vernacular%20architecture%2C%20it%20was%20done%20without%20a%20government%20banner%20overhanging%20the%20exhibit.%20The%20show%20raised%20a%20lot%20of%20eyebrows%20and%20asked%20questions%20about%20the%20relevance%20of%20such%20banal%20buildings%20inside%20a%20gallery%3B%20but%20nowhere%20was%20the%20exhibit%20derided%20as%20a%20waste%20of%20cultural%20resources.%20Would%20our%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%20consider%20placing%20a%202BHK%20builder%20flat%20in%20its%20main%20hall%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20state%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20architecture%3F%20Or%20would%20the%20IGNCA%20spend%20its%20budget%20on%20a%20display%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20mall%20buildings%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20Biennale%20exhibition%20does%20attempt%20to%20be%20broad-based%20by%20including%20works%20by%20some%20unknown%20artists%20in%20new%20mediums%2C%20its%20overall%20historical%20and%20cultural%20stance%20overshadows%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20more%20secular%20and%20inclusive%20perspective%20on%20art.%20While%20calling%20the%20show%20a%20celebration%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20art%2C%20architecture%20and%20design%2C%20its%20real%20intent%20it%20seems%20is%20to%20primarily%20showcase%20craft%20and%20promote%20the%20idea%20that%20valuable%20Indian%20art%20comes%20from%20a%20collective%20discipline%2C%20an%20effort%20directed%20towards%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20like%20stone%20carvers%20chiselling%20the%20panel%20of%20a%20temple%2C%20or%20bronze%20casters%20working%20on%20a%20religious%20statue.%20Doubtless%2C%20Indian%20temples%2C%20gardens%2C%20traditional%20doors%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebaolis%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20exhibit%20are%20a%20source%20of%20enormous%20cultural%20pride%2C%20and%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20show%20highlights%20the%20painstaking%20manner%20in%20which%20these%20architectural%20elements%20were%20constructed%20and%20crafted.%20But%20to%20call%20them%20all%20works%20of%20art%20wrongly%20presumes%20that%20everything%20accomplished%20before%20the%20British%20occupation%20had%20great%20artistic%20merit.%20Though%20finely%20crafted%2C%20many%20Rajasthani%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20doors%20and%20palace%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echattris%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20inherently%20unattractive%2C%20even%20ugly%3B%20many%20gardens%20and%20temples%20don%E2%80%99t%20qualify%20for%20inclusion%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20real%20problem%20of%20course%20remains%20with%20the%20sponsorship%20itself.%20However%20well-intentioned%20the%20government%2C%20the%20visible%20face%20behind%20art%20will%20always%20be%20suspect.%20Few%20federal%20governments%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20make%20so%20brazen%20a%20representation%20of%20themselves.%20Sadly%20when%20the%20Indian%20government%20gives%20money%20for%20art%2C%20it%20wants%20the%20public%20to%20not%20only%20know%2C%20but%20it%20must%20also%20select%20the%20work%20and%20showcase%20it%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20its%20own%20institutions.%20The%20Lalit%20Kala%20Academy%2C%20the%20Council%20of%20Architecture%2C%20the%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%2C%20and%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20are%20of%20course%20independent%20entities%2C%20with%20their%20independent%20voices.%20However%2C%20their%20artistic%20message%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20and%20should%20not%20be%20%E2%80%93%20in%20bureaucratic%20control.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20casual%20indifference%20to%20art%E2%80%99s%20complex%20reasoning%2C%20value%20and%20presentation%2C%20needs%20funding%20support%20that%20leaves%20the%20art%20and%20the%20artist%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20with%20so%20robust%20a%20showing%20for%20art%20at%20the%20Biennale%2C%20the%20government%20may%20opt%20for%20ventures%20into%20other%20arts.%20Soon%20enough%20there%20may%20be%20national%20events%20in%20stand-up%20comedy%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Great%20Indian%20Comedy%20Show%20%E2%80%93%20with%20jokes%20written%20and%20vetted%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20and%20another%20for%20theatre%20and%20films.%20With%20an%20audience%20so%20large%2C%20dispersed%20and%20mixed%20it%20may%20be%20good%20to%20know%20what%20is%20art%2C%20what%20is%20humour%2C%20and%20what%2C%20a%20good%20story.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fgautambhatiaarch%5C%22%3EGautam%20Bhatia%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20architect%20and%20sculptor.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702546159000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14121410%2FH20231208146124.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fart-architecture-design-biennale-government-support-politicisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20official%20endorsement%20by%20the%20government%20of%20what%20constitutes%20Indian%20art%20and%20design%20is%20not%20just%20troubling%20from%20the%20standpoint%20of%20its%20content%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20art%20should%20be%20so%20brazenly%20claimed%20by%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fart-architecture-design-biennale-government-support-politicisation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20There%20Is%20Silence%20in%20Kashmir%20Over%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20Verdict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F19161014%2FScreenshot-2022-10-19-at-4.10.07-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20the%20second%20Monday%20of%20December%20any%20different%3F%20Or%20did%20it%20have%20something%20new%20to%20offer%3F%20Well%20not%20for%20me%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20not%20for%20the%20millions%20of%20fellow%20Kashmiris%2C%20who%20live%20in%20Kashmir%20or%20like%20me%2C%20outside%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20us%20showed%20no%20shock%2C%20no%20surprise%2C%20just%20a%20little%20%E2%80%98I%20told%20you%20so%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98what%20else%20did%20you%20expect%3F%E2%80%99%20Because%20this%20is%20what%20was%20expected%2C%20nothing%20better%2C%20nothing%20newer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20homes%20were%20not%20chained%20this%20time.%20We%20were%20free%20to%20lodge%20protests.%20Did%20we%20take%20out%20grand%20protests%3F%20We%20did%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20does%20it%20mean%20we%20have%20reconciled%20collectively%3F%20Are%20we%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20say%20in%20things%20that%20define%20our%20political%20future%3F%20Reconciled%20that%20we%20have%20lost%20our%20voice%20and%20our%20voice%20does%20not%20matter%2C%20that%20we%20have%20no%20representation%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%3F%20We%20certainly%20have%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20for%20the%20last%20four%20and%20half%20years%2C%20our%20downgraded%20erstwhile%20state%20and%20now%20a%20Union%20territory%20has%20had%20no%20elected%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20last%20elections%20happened%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20nearly%20a%20decade%20ago.%20This%20is%20the%20longest%20ever%20stretch.%20The%20last%20time%20it%20happened%20was%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20militancy%2C%20when%201987%E2%80%99s%20famously%20rigged%20elections%20were%20followed%20in%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20may%20not%20see%20a%20functional%20democracy%20in%20many%20more%20years%20to%20come.%20We%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20can%20lose%20their%20jobs%20on%20mere%20charges%20of%20abetment%20of%20terrorism%2C%20stone%20pelting%20or%20any%20other%20family%20member%20being%20involved%20%E2%80%93%20even%20though%20the%20charges%20would%20not%20be%20strong%20enough%20to%20try%20them%20in%20courts%20of%20law.%20Social%20media%20posts%20can%20open%20the%20doors%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20every%20voice%20raised%20is%20%E2%80%98treachery%E2%80%99%2C%20every%20right%20asserted%20is%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20we%20can%20pray%20for%20people%20of%20Gaza%20in%20our%20hearts%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjk-authorities-seal-srinagars-jamia-masjid-to-prevent-pro-palestine-protests%5C%22%3Enot%20utter%20a%20word%20on%20the%20same%20in%20gatherings%20and%20mosques%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20our%20mosques%20and%20religious%20places%20can%20be%20locked%20for%20years%20together%2C%20and%20preachers%20barred%20from%20leading%20prayers.%20We%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20every%20few%20months%20there%20will%20be%20an%20amendment%20in%20previous%20laws%20or%20some%20new%20laws%20will%20be%20made%2C%20to%20strip%20us%20of%20our%20millenia-old%20identity%20even%20further.%20These%20include%20the%20domicile%20law%2C%20the%20changed%20land%20ownership%20rules%2C%20delimitation%20of%20electoral%20seats%20which%20takes%20the%20arithmetic%20across%20the%20mountains%2C%20to%20the%20liking%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%20The%20changes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20administration%20cadre%2C%20jobs%2C%20education%2C%20business%2C%20et%20al.%20We%20have%20seen%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FGVqpNulxkdc%3Fsi%3DHJ3CyGj3dns3Kh35%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20have%20we%20actually%20reconciled%20to%20it%20all%3F%20Have%20we%20given%20up%20or%20have%20we%20surrendered%20the%20right%20to%20dissent%3F%20The%20bad%20news%20is%20we%20have%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20silence%20in%20Kashmir%20is%20loud%20and%20deafening%20and%20its%20people%20are%20isolated.%20Kashmir%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20paradise%20it%20was%2C%20people%20continue%20to%20remain%20the%20best%20hosts%20you%20will%20have%20but%20we%20are%20far%20from%20happy.%20With%20every%20passing%20day%2C%20as%20the%20voices%20in%20Kashmir%20are%20muffled%2C%20we%20are%20stepping%20closer%20and%20closer%20to%20complete%20political%20alienation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20Kashmir%20remained%20unfazed.%20Its%20people%20believed%20that%20the%20court%20case%20was%20a%20lost%20battle%20from%20the%20word%20go.%20The%20way%20the%20honourable%20courts%20were%20batting%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20government%20during%20the%20hearing%20was%20indicative%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20right-minded%20people%20were%20posting%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20verdict%2C%20Kashmir%20was%20