stance%20on%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20revocation%20has%20become%20a%20war%20cry%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20too.%20The%20vote%20bank%20which%20the%20party%20appeals%20to%20will%20consider%20the%20verdict%20another%20victory%20in%20national%20interest.%20The%20WhatsApp%20forwards%20will%20now%20further%20cement%20the%20notions%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20managed%20to%20do%20what%20governments%20for%2070%20years%20failed%20to%20do%20%E2%80%93%20crush%20the%20political%20individualism%20of%20Muslim-majority%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20country%20where%20Muslims%20have%20become%20the%20%E2%80%98other%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20verdict%20once%20again%20satisfies%20the%20collective%20consciousness%20of%20the%20same%20political%20majority%20who%20feel%20centuries%20of%20Muslim%20rule%20in%20India%20needs%20to%20be%20avenged%20by%20these%20historic%20corrections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20of%20a%20Muslim-majority%20state%20acceding%20to%20secular%20India%20was%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20for%20common%20Kashmiris%20and%20crores%20of%20muslims%20in%20India.%20With%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20believing%20that%20president%20of%20India%20can%20unilaterally%20change%20constitutional%20character%20of%20a%20state%2C%20a%20wrong%20precedent%20has%20been%20set%20regarding%20the%20fluidity%20of%20guarantees%20that%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20provides%2C%20and%20Kashmir%20here%2C%20again%2C%20is%20just%20the%20laboratory%2C%20a%20test%20case%2C%20which%20can%20now%20be%20unleashed%20anywhere%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToufiq%20Rashid%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20covered%20the%20Kashmir%20conflict%2C%20health%20and%20wellbeing%20for%20top%20Indian%20newspapers%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20She%20now%20works%20at%20%40Pixstory.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702542920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F19161014%2FScreenshot-2022-10-19-at-4.10.07-